### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/admin/requests
@submissionId = 1

### Get all requests
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get request KPIs
GET {{baseUrl}}/kpis

### Approve a request (without comments)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{submissionId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Approve a request (with comments)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{submissionId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewComments": "All documentation is complete and verified. Organization meets all requirements."
}

### Reject a request (without comments)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{submissionId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Reject a request (with comments)
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{submissionId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewComments": "Missing required documentation for carbon inventory verification."
}
